                                                                        \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2023/09/garmin-epix-pro-hero-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2023/09/garmin-epix-pro-hero-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2023/09/garmin-epix-pro-hero-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2023/09/garmin-epix-pro-hero-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"2048\" height=\"1336\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Garmin Epix Pro\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2023/09/garmin-epix-pro-hero-1.png\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2023/09/garmin-epix-pro-hero-1.png\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/garmin-epix-pro-gen-2-review/\" title=\"Garmin Epix Pro (Gen 2) review: It\u0026#39;s worth the money\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\tGarmin Epix Pro (Gen 2) review: It\u0026#39;s worth the money\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eThe second-gen Epix Pro brings some welcomed changes\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAnd while this particular model has a retail price of $1,100, you can now score a hefty discount that knocks $410 off, dropping it down to its lowest price to date at $690. You won\u0026#39;t find a better price than what we\u0026#39;re seeing now. And you also won\u0026#39;t regret picking this model up if you\u0026#39;re looking to really get a better grasp of your daily workouts.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"what-39-s-great-about-the-garmin-epix-pro-gen-2\"\u003e\n                        What\u0026#39;s great about the Garmin Epix Pro (Gen 2)?\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n    \n    \n    \n\u003cp\u003eThe first thing you should probably know about this watch is that it is a bit larger, coming in at 51mm. However, you also get a large and beautiful AMOLED screen, along with an impressive battery life that can last up to 31 days. In addition, the watch is built to be extremely durable, with a fiber-reinforced polymer case, titanium rear cover, and sapphire screen.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eIt should come as no surprise that the watch has a wealth of sensors, making it possible to track the most important details of your workout. And there\u0026#39;s even a Garmin Coach that can help you train better, in order to meet your specific goals. Furthermore, you can also get GPS tracking for your runs, walks, or even hikes. And there\u0026#39;s built-in safety and tracking features as well.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eSince this is a smartwatch, you\u0026#39;ll be able to get notifications on your wrist, and be able to make payments at compatible tap to pay terminals as well. Overall, this watch really does it all and makes it easy to track your health and fitness metrics that matter. Get it now for its best price yet while this deal\u0026#39;s still around.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e\n                                    \u003cli\u003e\n                    \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/wearables/\" title=\"Smartwatches \u0026amp; Wearables\"\u003e\n                                                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://static0.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/google-pixel-watch-3-1.jpg?q=50\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=32\u0026amp;h=32\u0026amp;dpr=1.5\" alt=\"Smartwatches \u0026amp; Wearables\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"/\u003e\n                        \u003c/p\u003e\n                                            \u003cp\u003eSmartwatches \u0026amp; Wearables\u003c/p\u003e\n                    \u003c/a\u003e\n                \u003c/li\u003e\n                            \u003cli\u003e\n                    \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/tag/garmin-epix-pro-2nd-gen/\" title=\"Garmin Epix Pro (2nd Gen)\"\u003e